29
00:00:49,910 --> 00:00:50,440
My...

30
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:51,680
Počula som niečo o slonici.

31
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:52,110
Chrám!

32
00:00:52,110 --> 00:00:53,240
Pôjdeme nakŕmiť slonice do chrámu.

33
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,040
Slonice

34
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:54,970
