37
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:57,600
A kto vás k nim zoberie?

38
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,280
Mama?

39
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,350
Pôjdeme iba s mamou.

40
00:00:59,350 --> 00:01:00,970
Berie nás moja mama.

41
00:01:00,970 --> 00:01:02,110
Pete!

42
