Kam to ide?

47
00:01:12,730 --> 00:01:14,150
Čo sa to deje?

48
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:44,820
Prečo plačem?

49
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,840
Prečo?

50
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:53,970
Zabudni naňho.

51
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:55,460
Postav sa

52
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:57,860
a choď domov.

53
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:08,800
Prečo to tak bolí?

54
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,840
Už ťa nenechám nikam odísť.

55
00:02:25,310 --> 00:02:26,150
Ae?

56
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,440
Prečo si predo mnou utekal?

57
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,150
Vieš, ako dlho som ťa hľadal?

58
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:36,110
Čo tu robíš, Ae?

59
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,800
